  <brief_title>Use of Topical Benzocaine for Analgesia in Lingual Frenotomy of the Newborn</brief_title>
  <official_title>Time of Cry After Lingual Frenotomy in Infants With Lingual Frenulum and Breastfeeding Difficulties, With or Without Use of Topical Benzocaine Analgesia</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Tel-Aviv Sourasky Medical Center</agency>
